name: Midnight Jesters of the Blossom
description: Hailing from the Bogs of the <Anuran Countryside>, the Midnight Jesters of the Blossom are known for their strength, vitality, and good fortune. Now serving as guards-for-hire using their high-tech defensive equipment, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
